, NHMUK PI BZ 8767, Aubeterre Fm, Pointe de Suzac, Meschers; 
<emphasis id="2698D703920EFFC9FAACFA6CE96DF9B9" bold="true" box="[1312,1325,1535,1552]" pageId="9" pageNumber="522">B</emphasis>
